### Solution transfer component

comp-solution-transfer-fill-normal = Napełniasz { $target } ilością { $amount }u z { $owner }.
comp-solution-transfer-fill-fully = Napełniasz { $target } po brzegi ilością { $amount }u z { $owner }.
comp-solution-transfer-transfer-solution = Przenosisz { $amount }u do { $target }.

## Displayed when trying to transfer to a solution, but either the giver is empty or the taker is full

comp-solution-transfer-is-empty = { CAPITALIZE($target) } jest pusty!
comp-solution-transfer-is-full = { CAPITALIZE($target) } jest pełny!

## Displayed in change transfer amount verb's name

comp-solution-transfer-verb-custom-amount = Własna
comp-solution-transfer-verb-amount = { $amount }u
comp-solution-transfer-verb-toggle = Przełącz na { $amount }u

## Displayed after you successfully change a solution's amount using the BUI

comp-solution-transfer-set-amount = Ustawiono przenoszoną ilość na { $amount }u.
comp-solution-transfer-set-amount-max = Maks.: { $amount }u
comp-solution-transfer-set-amount-min = Min.: { $amount }u
